{
  "stem": "942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were just wooden planks there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were five of us on a bunk, naked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And morning arrived very-- just a little while after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we heard a gong, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was a lager gong, you know, that they-- it was like a big bell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this meant that you had to get out of your bunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were lined up and counted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they came with a metal container.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was some liquid on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was called morning tea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It looked like tea, but it was-- it didn't taste like tea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we-- we received a metal dish-- it was called a schissel in German-- that we were drinking this tea from.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You had to line up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the one guy was ladling it in into these schissels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And you know, we-- we were drinking it, because we had no spoons, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no spoons or forks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You just had a schissel, and that's the way we ate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You always drank from this pot, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So when these guys brought the tea, we asked them, what happened to our families?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So they said, well-- at that time, we looked around, and we saw in the little distance away, this huge building that had flames and smoke coming out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't know what this building was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We could smell something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a very bad smell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was like burning-- I remember, you know, from the blacksmith at home, when he was shoeing horses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And you know, when they put the hot shoe on the horse's hooves, it was smelling like-- you know, like burning flesh.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that was the smell that was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well, you see, they went up in smoke.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
